 29/12/18 On the whole this was a wet day and far from pleasant . A visit to the mess this morn show that window had suffer from revel last night and there were a few sore head and pale face in the morn . It is a good thing the day is Sunday . Afternoon Baze call in a car from Divis on his way to Walcourt and told us that the Bde .HQ had got home alright . The mount of our guard was an attract that drew a good crowd this afternoon but some of the younger N.C.Os need a good deal of instruct in their duti . Wrote and read . It was dark at 3.30 pm ? I must take more exercis than at present . Our villag is veri quiet today .
